#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:89
msgid "For this activity, the breakout groups will work together to examine information gathered in a survey and will then determine how to map that information to the DwC-DP tables."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/nodes/modules/ROOT/pages/gnt-emerging-publishing-models.adoc:91
msgid "Step 1: Each group member will be assigned a role and should read through their provided role descriptions:"
